      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[575ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[750ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>to the pan and bring to the boil</p>",
