    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped basa </strong>to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for an initial 2-3 min</p>",
