    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p><p>After an initial 2-3 min, add the<strong> spinach </strong>to the pan with the basa and cook, covered, for a further 2 min or until the spinach has started to wilt and the basa is cooked through – this your <strong>curried basa, cherry tomato & spinach soup</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
